This article showcases news, blog posts, and updates that VRChat published between January 1, 2017 and December 31, 2017.
==History==

Since 2016, VRChat's developer updates have been posted on several outlets, and have also gone through different names. Former developer updates have been called ''Developer Blogs'', ''Community Updates'', and ''Town Hall Meetings''.

VRChat published their blog posts on ''[https://medium.com/@vrchat Medium]'' starting in April 2016, and published their patchnotes from 2016 on their former domain, ''vrchat.net''.
<br>Patch notes for VRChat ''Builds released before February 28, 2018''<ref>[https://docs.vrchat.com/docs/patch-notes-pre-2018 "Patch Notes - Pre-2018"] on ''[[docs.vrchat.com]]''. Retrieved September 6, 2024.</ref> can be viewed [https://docs.vrchat.com/docs/patch-notes-pre-2018 here].
